data.description: Assumable VA Loan at 2.8%...Welcome home!!  Here is approximately 2250 sqft of rural living at its best.   Bay windows and a garden window in the kitchen make this home a very warm and friendly place to enjoy life.  The fourth bedroom and third bath create a possible mother-in-law setup.  This 1.1 ac property located in Yosemite Lakes Park has been well taken care of and the home has many upgrades.  The home has 4 bedrooms and 3 baths and a three car garage AND a 26x26 steel shop building.  The insulated shop building has a 14' roll up door together with a walk-in door and has both 110 and 220 outlets with a 100 amp service.  There is an RV hookup outside the shop building.  Also included is an 8x14 utility shed for the landscaping equipment.  Irrigation of the landscaping is taken care of with automatic sprinklers.  The stand-alone wood stove in the living area more than keeps the home warm.  The kitchen and bathrooms have numerous upgrades and improvements as listed on the attached listing information.  Large bedrooms with a Jack n Jill bathroom finish off the inside.  The attached three-car garage is finished inside   Accent lighting and a gas firepit on the back porch create a great place to spend evenings as well as a nice place to start the day just drinking coffee.  This home is all part of the Yosemite Lakes Park that offers a 9-hole golf course with a pro shop and cafe.  Also included is a swimming pool. tennis courts, rec center and equestrian center.
